source('../jma/jma_class_2.r')
jma_data <- Jma$new('./')
allData <- jma_data$allData()

# allData %>% filter(place=酒田) %>% group_by(start_m) %>% mutate(rain_month = sum(降水量_平年値 %>% as.character() %>% as.numeric()))
# allData %<>% group_by(start_y) %>% mutate(降雪積算=cumsum(降雪量合計))
allData %>% select(place) %>% unique()
# thisPlace = '尾花沢'
padding_date <- function(str){
  result <- str_sub(str_c('0',str), start = -2, end = -1)
  return(result)
}

# m_d(月_日)
thisPlaceData <- allData %>% mutate(m_d = str_c(start_m %>% padding_date, start_d %>% padding_date,sep='/') %>% as.character()) 
# 
thisPlaceData <- thisPlaceData %>% mutate(
  display_ymd = paste('2025',start_m %>% as.character,start_d %>% as.character,sep='-') %>% as.Date
)
# 年毎に降水量積算
start_m_d <- '2025-06-01'
# start_m_d <- '2025-06-15'
# start_m_d <- '2025-07-01'
# start_m_d <- '2025-07-15'
thisPlaceData2 <- thisPlaceData %>% filter(display_ymd >= start_m_d %>% as.Date) %>% arrange(st_date) %>% group_by(start_y) %>% mutate(降水積算=cumsum(降水量))

# allData %>% filter(place=='酒田')
# paste("place=='", thisPlace, "'", sep = '')

y_axis = '最低気温'
exp_ = sym(y_axis)
thisPlaceData2 <- thisPlaceData2 %>% mutate({{ y_axis }} := (!!exp_) %>% as.numeric)
thisPlaceData2
